  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7, then take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Cut your <strong>potato[es]</strong> (skins on) into <strong>chips</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chips</strong> to one side of a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray (or two!) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1688115315165-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1688115315165-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1688115315165-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1688115315165-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1688115315165-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and grate your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>chicken thighs</strong> to a bowl with <strong>half </strong>the <strong>grated garlic </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), <strong>dried oregano</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> and mix it all together</p><p>Add the <strong>marinated chicken</strong> to the other side of the baking tray[s] and put the tray[s] in the oven for 20-25 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the chips are golden and crisp</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1688115318424-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1688115318424-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
