          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1688115318424-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1688115318424-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1688115318424-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and slice your <strong>red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>sliced red onion[s]</strong> to a small bowl with your <strong>red wine vinegar</strong> and a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> and set aside to pickle – this is your <strong>quick-pickled onion</strong></p><p>Cut 2 slices per person from the <strong>tomato[es]</strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>remaining tomato </strong>finely</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1688115321269-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1688115321269-x400.jpg",
