          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1688115324863-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>halloumi</strong> into 4 sticks per person</p><p>Add the <strong>halloumi sticks</strong> to a plate with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour </strong>and turn several times until fully coated</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated halloumi</strong> and cook for 2-3 min on each side or until golden and crispy – these are your <strong>halloumi fries</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1688115328081-x200.jpg",
