            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>honey </strong>and <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to a small bowl and stir it all together – this is your <strong>hot honey</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>pizza base[s] </strong>to a baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 3-5 min or until warmed through</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 3 or more? Use 2 trays!</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1688115331034-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1688115331034-x400.jpg",
