          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1688115331034-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once cooked, transfer the <strong>cooked chicken</strong> to a clean board and slice into strips</p><p>To build your gyros, spread a dollop of <strong>tzatziki</strong> on the <strong>warmed pizza base </strong>and top with the <strong>tomato rounds</strong>, <strong>chips</strong>, <strong>sliced chicken </strong>and some of the <strong>quick-pickled onion</strong> – this is your <strong>chicken gyros</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>sliced cucumber</strong> and <strong>chopped tomato</strong> to the <strong>remaining quick-pickled onion</strong> and toss – this is your <strong>Greek-style salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
