            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve your <strong>chicken gyros </strong>with the <strong>halloumi fries</strong>, <strong>Greek-style salad</strong> and <strong>remaining tzatziki </strong>to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>hot honey </strong>over the halloumi fries</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
